Some Untested Classes¶

These classes have been written for different projects and are not tested to be compatible with the current state of CSI. Everything can be imported, but we do not guarantee they will properly interact with other classes. Some of them will, some of them will not…

  • dippingfault class
  • faultwithdip class
  • faultwithvaryingdip class
  • planarfault class
